"{\n    \"Title\": \"December 31, 2012 and 2011Notes to the consolidated financial statements\",\n    \"row 1\": \"(in thousands of dollars)\",\n    \"row 2\": \"2. Significant accounting policies (continued)\",\n    \"row 3\": \"Legal provisions\",\n    \"row 4\": \"Provisions are recognized when the Port Authority has a present obligation (legal or constructive) as a\",\n    \"row 5\": \"result of a past event, it is probable that the Port Authority will be required to settle the obligation, and a\",\n    \"row 6\": \"reliable estimate can be made of the amount of the obligation.\",\n    \"row 7\": \"The amount recognized as a provision is the best estimate of the consideration required to settle the\",\n    \"row 8\": \"present obligation at the end of the reporting period, taking into account the risks and uncertainties\",\n    \"row 9\": \"surrounding the obligation.\",\n    \"row 10\": \"Please see details in Note 12.\",\n    \"row 11\": \"Tunnel concession liability\",\n    \"row 12\": \"The accounting treatment for the tunnel project including the related asset under construction and\",\n    \"row 13\": \"concession liability was a key area of judgement. Port Authority reviewed the substance of the Project\",\n    \"row 14\": \"Agreement and concluded that the present value of the tunnel\\u2019s construction costs and related liability\",\n    \"row 15\": \"should be recognized on a percentage of completion bases. See details in Note 16.\",\n    \"row 16\": \"3. Accounts receivable\",\n    \"row 17\": \"2012 2011\",\n    \"row 18\": \"Trade accounts receivable, net of allowance for\",\n    \"row 19\": \"doubtful accounts 6,227 5,113\",\n    \"row 20\": \"Airport capital assistance program receivable - 871\",\n    \"row 21\": \"Mortgage receivable, interest at 9%, matured July 1, 2012 - 66\",\n    \"row 22\": \"Deposits 12 12\",\n    \"row 23\": \"6,239 6,062\",\n    \"row 24\": \"4, Long-term investments\",\n    \"row 25\": \"2012 2011\",\n    \"row 26\": \"